{
  "texts": [
    "This hinders the timely execution of dynamic updates essential for maintaining seamless connectivity.",
    "To address this limitation of metatransformers inherent in [5], we propose the use of data filtering.",
    "As discussed next, this data filtering approach, aims to convey a condensed sequence of pertinent information to the LMM.",
    "To achieve this, we propose to start with the identification of physical symbols present across the multimodal data.",
    "Physical symbols here refer to abstract entities present in the data that have relevant semantics with respect to the wireless network."
  ]
}